OL,4,Calcohol: Official advice if UK loses
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FDetails have emerged on the advice
OL,8,Fgiven to Britons in the event of a
OL,9,Fmajor national power blackout,
OL,10,Fincluding on how to ration food and
OL,11,Fwater.
OL,13,FThe government has published the
OL,14,Flengthy scripts that would be read out
OL,15,Fon the radio by Chris Whitty and other
OL,16,Fchief medical officers in the event of
OL,17,Fa UK-wide power outage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
