OL,7,FWhile the prospect is "very unlikely",
OL,8,Fefforts to make the UK better prepared
OL,9,Fhave ramped up after Spain and
OL,10,FPortugal were hit with blackouts in
OL,11,FApril.
OL,13,FThe government says such an outage
OL,14,Fwould cause "significant and
OL,15,Fwidespread disruption and risk to
OL,16,Fhealth."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
