OL,7,FThe messages from the chief medical
OL,8,Fofficers would be read out on BBC
OL,9,FRadio 2 and Radio 4 and accessed via
OL,10,Fbattery-powered radios, because other
OL,11,Fcommunications infrastructure would be
OL,12,Fwiped out.
OL,14,FThe address begins by saying: "I am
OL,15,Fabout to provide you with important
OL,16,Finformation. You may want to write
OL,17,Fthis down so that you can refer to it
OL,18,Flater. This advice will be repeated
OL,19,Fregularly.
