OL,7,FThe first script begins with advice on
OL,8,Fdaily water intake and ways to ration
OL,9,Fwater.
OL,11,FPeople should drink at least two
OL,12,Flitres of fluid a day, which is around
OL,13,Feight cups. Tap water is safe from the
OL,14,Fcold tap as long as it is flowing
OL,15,Fnormally.
OL,17,FOther fluids considered safe to drink
OL,18,Finclude bottled water, soft and fizzy
OL,19,Fdrinks and juice from tinned fruit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
