OL,7,FIn the event of a power outage, the
OL,8,Fsewage system won't be working,
OL,9,Fmeaning people can't flush the toilet.
OL,11,F"You should collect your poo in
OL,12,Fplastic bags, which should be sealed
OL,13,Fand disposed of with normal household
OL,14,Fwaste, ideally in an outside bin," the
OL,15,Fadvice says.
OL,17,FAlcoholic drinks should also be
OL,18,Favoided because they're dehydrating,
OL,19,Fpeople would be told.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
