OL,7,FIn the event of tap water and other
OL,8,Ffluids running out, the advice
OL,9,Frecommends sourcing water from
OL,10,Frainwater collection, such as water
OL,11,Fbutts, reservoirs and lakes and then
OL,12,Ffiltering and purifying it.
OL,14,FThe messages would say you can filter
OL,15,Fwater using a coffee filter, a
OL,16,Fpillowcase, or a bed sheet.
OL,18,FThe water can then be disinfected by
OL,19,Fboiling it, using water purification
OL,20,Ftablets or adding a small amount of
OL,21,Fbleach to the water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
