OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"You can use regular unscented,
OL,13,Fhousehold bleach. It is important not
OL,14,Fto use too much bleach. Add
OL,15,Fapproximately one-quarter of a
OL,16,Fteaspoon of unscented, household
OL,17,Fbleach for every 10 litres of water
OL,18,F(approximately one bucket). Leave it
OL,19,Fto stand for 15 minutes," the advice
OL,20,Fsays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
