OL,7,FThe chief medical officer would also
OL,8,Fsay: "I know all the advice I am
OL,9,Fgiving you might sound strange and you
OL,10,Fmay be especially worried about
OL,11,Fdrinking water containing bleach.
OL,13,F"Remember that this advice has been
OL,14,Fdeveloped by doctors and scientists to
OL,15,Fhelp keep you safe and healthy, as
OL,16,Flong as you follow these instructions
OL,17,Fcarefully."
OL,19,FFood: eat cupboard products and use a
OL,20,Fcamping stove
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
