OL,7,FThe advice also directs people to eat
OL,8,Fchilled and frozen food likely to go
OL,9,Foff quickly first, and to save
OL,10,Fcupboard items with a longer shelf
OL,11,Flife until last.
OL,13,F"Take stock of how much food you have
OL,14,Favailable for everyone in your
OL,15,Fhousehold for the next few days," the
OL,16,Fscript says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
