OL,7,F"Do not eat food that is rotting -
OL,8,Fthrow it away immediately in an
OL,9,Foutside bin. Open the fridge and
OL,10,Ffreezer doors as little as possible to
OL,11,Fkeep them cold."
OL,13,FIn winter, people will be able to keep
OL,14,Ffood outside in a sealed container to
OL,15,Fkeep it cold."Food might take longer
OL,16,Fto cook than usual so make sure it is
OL,17,Fsteaming hot and cooked through before
OL,18,Fyou eat it," the script says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
