OL,7,FThe advice suggests using a camping
OL,8,Fstove or a barbecue outside to cook,
OL,9,For even lighting a campfire. Although
OL,10,Fit says they must not be used inside
OL,11,Fbecause of the risk of carbon monoxide
OL,12,Fpoisoning.
OL,14,FYou can visit the government's Prepare
OL,15,Fwebsite to get practical advice on how
OL,16,Fto deal with a power cut.
